op. cit.,</i> footnote 14, Article 12. 
</p>
<p> 79 <i>UNCAT,</i> <i>op. cit.,</i> footnote 14, <i>United Nations Convention on Enforced Disappearances, op. cit.,</i> 
footnote 14, Article 11(1). 
