footnote 99<i>, </i>para. 82; ECtHR, <i>A. and Others v. United Kingdom</i>, application No. 3455/05, Judgment 
at paras. 218 to 220; Case T-85/09 <i>Yassin Abdullah Kadi v. European Commission</i>, General Court 
(Seventh Chamber), 30 September 2010 [2011] CMLR 24, paras. 173 to 174; <i>Home Secretary v. AF 
(No. 3) </i>[2010] AC 289. 
